/>\n<br />\n睇心情佢講唔講  冇路捉"},{"pid":"ebe66644855021b906336c289a7a5bed2a86e26e","tid":2189701,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"羅馬迦太基戰爭"},{"pid":"c01dbf9f0a66f5fd8254653f054ff2a27d4c9f11","tid":2189701,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf1e45d4816d9276a2b0ca77b7c9025bc6bbe8bd","tid":2189701,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:40:07.000Z","msg":"暗渡陳倉？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"常被誤寫為「暗渡陳倉」，正確寫法是「暗度陳倉」是兵法三十六計的第八計。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><br />\n即在戰爭中隱蔽攻擊路線，暗中迂迴到敵後偷襲，攻其不備，克敵制勝。<br />\n</span><br />\n陳倉是古地名，今為陝西省寶雞市。 原文為：「示之以動，利其靜而有主，益動而巽。」此計是我方利用敵人被我方佯攻、佯動的迷惑手段所蒙蔽，乘虛而入，以達到軍事上的出奇制勝。"},{"pid":"eee5fbba91a2135a7c28f6dbadbcd7c28f372fe7","tid":2189701,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a68df39b4e8c38d3cbf8ea5edf1b8739d102914","tid":2189701,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7036299b87f60abccd3ed934546f15f6fcfc7edf","tid":2189701,"uid":23173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f440725a6de33e53421eeffb664a2a4a474a0ac3","tid":2189701,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:35:57.000Z","msg":"寫緊篇文章，想搵reference :<br />\n<br />\n即係通常呢啲情況係敵強我弱，不能正面交鋒<br />\n<br />\n好奇軍事歷史上有先咩著名嘅戰略？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"建議你睇華杉註的孫子兵法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"有無啲聲東擊西嘅策略？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:44:45.000Z","msg":"明修棧道 暗渡陳倉囉"},{"pid":"f89a0029a32872786c35b01a46c4ed25f3db0b6a","tid":2189701,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ndXuRoJd6hQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DndXuRoJd6hQ&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs41GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=89831d8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.y